1
00:00:00,370 --> 00:00:01,370
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:01,440 --> 00:00:03,210
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,270 --> 00:00:05,240
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:09,710 --> 00:00:11,350
(The late Kim Dan Hui)

5
00:00:11,380 --> 00:00:12,550
(Name: Kim Myung Hui)

6
00:00:12,620 --> 00:00:13,850
(Date of Birth:
October 14, 1973, Age 52)

7
00:00:19,920 --> 00:00:21,330
The person who was Kim Dan Hui...

8
00:00:22,190 --> 00:00:23,900
is now living as Kim Myung Hui.

9
00:00:25,500 --> 00:00:29,070
She killed off her old self
to live as someone else.

10
00:00:31,140 --> 00:00:34,570
Just like I killed off Baek Jin Ju
to become Chloe?

11
00:00:37,240 --> 00:00:39,040
(The late Kim Dan Hui)

12
00:00:47,890 --> 00:00:49,590
You've been pushing yourself
too hard.

13
00:00:49,990 --> 00:00:50,990
You need to rest.

14
00:00:51,320 --> 00:00:52,320
I'm fine.

15
00:00:53,160 --> 00:00:55,530
There's the whole Chloe situation,
and so much else to do.

16
00:00:55,730 --> 00:00:57,900
That's exactly why you need to take
better care of yourself.

17
00:01:11,610 --> 00:01:14,410
Manager Kang says
you're not feeling well.

18
00:01:14,980 --> 00:01:16,250
I'm just a little under the weather.

19
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:18,350
I think she's been
under a lot of stress...

20
00:01:18,380 --> 00:01:20,320
from rescuing
and looking after you, sir.

21
00:01:24,620 --> 00:01:26,860
It won't affect my work
at the office.

22
00:01:27,590 --> 00:01:29,130
Once the board
approves the resolution,

23
00:01:29,660 --> 00:01:31,900
I will begin my duties
as acting chairman.

24
00:01:34,470 --> 00:01:35,470
About that...

25
00:01:38,240 --> 00:01:39,740
It would be best
to put that on hold.

26
00:01:43,010 --> 00:01:45,440
Manager Kang was right.

27
00:01:46,340 --> 00:01:48,110
I wonder why he suddenly
changed his mind.

28
00:01:50,350 --> 00:01:51,380
On hold?

29
00:01:52,150 --> 00:01:53,650
Did I do something wrong?

30
00:01:54,220 --> 00:01:55,290
What's the reason?

31
00:02:17,310 --> 00:02:18,310
(Kim Myung Hui knows...)

32
00:02:18,380 --> 00:02:19,380
(you killed Baek Jun Gi
of Temi Bio.)

33
00:02:27,920 --> 00:02:28,920
Kim Myung Hui knows...

34
00:02:29,790 --> 00:02:32,690
you killed Baek Jun Gi of Temi Bio.

35
00:02:33,490 --> 00:02:34,490
What's this?

36
00:02:37,160 --> 00:02:38,560
Hyun Jun brought it to me.

37
00:02:47,470 --> 00:02:49,010
I went to see my mother
in the basement,

38
00:02:49,610 --> 00:02:50,940
and she asked me
to give this to you.

39
00:02:51,340 --> 00:02:53,810
She said she should
at least tell you this, Father.

40
00:03:01,190 --> 00:03:02,190
Did you read...

41
00:03:03,690 --> 00:03:04,690
what it said?

42
00:03:05,190 --> 00:03:06,760
Despite not having any tools,

43
00:03:06,820 --> 00:03:08,160
she still managed
to seal it tightly.

44
00:03:08,930 --> 00:03:10,400
I didn't want to open something...

45
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:12,300
she had obviously sealed
for a reason.

46
00:03:18,100 --> 00:03:20,310
Did you pretend to be on my side...

47
00:03:20,670 --> 00:03:21,770
while knowing about Baek Jun Gi,

48
00:03:22,610 --> 00:03:26,380
deceiving and using me all along?

49
00:03:29,310 --> 00:03:30,620
Tell me the truth.

50
00:03:31,050 --> 00:03:32,480
What in the world
is this supposed to mean?

51
00:03:32,980 --> 00:03:35,820
Oh Jung Ran is trying to frame me,

52
00:03:36,420 --> 00:03:37,690
even if it means making you look
like a murderer.

53
00:03:38,060 --> 00:03:41,290
Don't tell me you fell
for such a pathetic lie,

54
00:03:42,090 --> 00:03:45,700
and now you think I believe
you're a murderer.

55
00:03:50,640 --> 00:03:54,870
I'm so disappointed.
No, I'm honestly furious.

56
00:03:55,710 --> 00:03:57,010
You believed Oh Jung Ran,

57
00:03:57,080 --> 00:03:58,180
the woman who tried to kill you,

58
00:03:58,510 --> 00:04:00,350
and yet you doubt me,
the one who saved your life.

59
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:03,920
Wait. Are you...

60
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:06,280
angry at me?

61
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:08,120
How could you do this to me?

62
00:04:09,050 --> 00:04:11,720
Oh Jung Ran is down in the basement,

63
00:04:12,060 --> 00:04:15,260
scheming about how to escape
and drive a wedge between us.

64
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:19,560
And you fall for her pathetic lies
and doubt me?

65
00:04:20,670 --> 00:04:23,640
Whatever. I've no interest
in being the acting chairman.

66
00:04:36,550 --> 00:04:39,650
Oh Jung Ran was just
pulling a stunt...

67
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:41,150
to drive us apart?

68
00:04:42,750 --> 00:04:45,290
I should've known better
than to trust her.

69
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:49,390
That Oh Jung Ran is unbelievable.

70
00:04:56,770 --> 00:04:59,200
Oh Jung Ran is really
something else.

71
00:04:59,470 --> 00:05:01,940
She's framing you
even while locked in the basement.

72
00:05:03,610 --> 00:05:04,610
Park Hyun Jun, Chloe...

73
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:06,380
The three of them are
as thick as thieves.

74
00:05:06,640 --> 00:05:07,980
Unbelievable.

75
00:05:09,710 --> 00:05:11,950
You managed to get past it this time
by claiming it was a setup,

76
00:05:12,180 --> 00:05:13,790
but what if Chairman Park
remains suspicious?

77
00:05:15,190 --> 00:05:16,820
He's already suspicious
of Min Jun...

78
00:05:16,890 --> 00:05:18,590
because of the Temi Bio documentary.

79
00:05:18,860 --> 00:05:20,790
Shouldn't we strike back at them?

80
00:05:21,090 --> 00:05:22,090
You're right.

81
00:05:22,930 --> 00:05:24,930
Oh Jung Ran, Park Hyun Jun,
and Chloe.

82
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:27,770
I need to cut the ties
between those three.

83
00:05:28,970 --> 00:05:30,170
I'll start with Chloe.

84
00:05:33,640 --> 00:05:36,140
President Kim Myung Hui
is a very good liar.

85
00:05:36,870 --> 00:05:38,510
She'll probably fool
Chairman Park again...

86
00:05:38,580 --> 00:05:39,740
and get off the hook.

87
00:05:40,550 --> 00:05:43,280
In any case, the acting chairman
appointment is on hold.

88
00:05:43,550 --> 00:05:44,550
That buys us some time.

89
00:05:44,950 --> 00:05:46,320
What about Kim Dan Hui?

90
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:47,890
Have you found anything?

91
00:05:49,320 --> 00:05:51,590
I'm still looking into it.

92
00:05:52,360 --> 00:05:53,620
I'll get back to you.

93
00:05:58,600 --> 00:06:00,160
(The late Kim Dan Hui,
Name: Kim Myung Hui)

94
00:06:01,170 --> 00:06:02,970
Until I find out for sure,

95
00:06:04,270 --> 00:06:06,040
I have to keep it a secret for now.

96
00:06:08,310 --> 00:06:09,340
Kim Dan Hui...

97
00:06:10,340 --> 00:06:13,180
How did you become Kim Myung Hui?

98
00:06:14,350 --> 00:06:16,480
It looks like Oh Jung Ran
and Chairman Park...

99
00:06:16,550 --> 00:06:17,650
don't know yet.

100
00:06:21,590 --> 00:06:23,920
(The late Kim Dan Hui,
Oct 14, 1973 - Oct 7, 1997)

101
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:27,930
I need to find out
what happened 30 years ago.

102
00:06:33,730 --> 00:06:34,930
Get in here.

103
00:06:35,570 --> 00:06:37,970
Sit down. Go on, have a seat.

104
00:06:39,100 --> 00:06:41,870
I told you I wasn't eating.
Stop bothering me.

105
00:06:42,370 --> 00:06:45,680
Are you trying to starve yourself
to death for real?

106
00:06:46,380 --> 00:06:49,410
That's right. You have to live
to fight another day.

107
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:50,550
Good grief.

108
00:06:51,980 --> 00:06:53,320
Just have one bite, okay?

109
00:06:54,550 --> 00:06:55,620
Come on, just eat.

110
00:06:58,720 --> 00:07:00,020
Unbelievable.

111
00:07:01,630 --> 00:07:02,630
You...

112
00:07:03,660 --> 00:07:05,830
It's time
you gave it to us straight.

113
00:07:06,230 --> 00:07:07,600
Why would you pull
a stunt like that?

114
00:07:07,870 --> 00:07:11,270
Is it really because
Park Min Jun wanted to break up?

115
00:07:13,740 --> 00:07:15,270
What does it matter why I did it?

116
00:07:15,570 --> 00:07:16,570
What?

117
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:18,710
Then what matters?

118
00:07:18,880 --> 00:07:22,180
That Park Min Jun
will never take my side.

119
00:07:22,350 --> 00:07:24,420
That he doesn't care if I die.

120
00:07:24,420 --> 00:07:25,450
What?

121
00:07:25,980 --> 00:07:28,850
That worthless jerk.

122
00:07:29,390 --> 00:07:32,120
Forget it, okay? Yu Na, from now on,

123
00:07:32,390 --> 00:07:34,060
just forget all about
a scumbag like that.

124
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:36,060
No matter the reason,

125
00:07:36,060 --> 00:07:37,500
anyone who can be that cold...

126
00:07:37,500 --> 00:07:39,730
to someone saying
they're going to die...

127
00:07:39,730 --> 00:07:41,170
is rotten to the core.

128
00:07:42,030 --> 00:07:44,740
Could he have known
we were putting on an act...

129
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:46,200
and said that on purpose?

130
00:07:46,270 --> 00:07:49,240
If he had realized that,
he wouldn't have left quietly.

131
00:07:49,770 --> 00:07:51,410
He would've made a huge fuss...

132
00:07:51,410 --> 00:07:53,040
and asked what we thought
we were doing.

133
00:07:54,110 --> 00:07:55,850
If that's how Min Jun
is going to be,

134
00:07:56,610 --> 00:07:57,880
then I have no choice.

135
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:58,950
What?

136
00:07:59,550 --> 00:08:01,390
As much as I like Park Min Jun,

137
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:04,290
I can't just throw
my whole life away.

138
00:08:06,690 --> 00:08:11,130
I'll protect myself first,
even if it means fighting him.

139
00:08:12,260 --> 00:08:16,430
- You'll fight him?
- What do you mean you'll fight him?

140
00:08:18,170 --> 00:08:19,170
What...

141
00:08:22,970 --> 00:08:26,480
That's right. You have to eat
if you're going to fight.

142
00:08:26,540 --> 00:08:27,550
Eat up.

143
00:08:27,850 --> 00:08:28,980
Good for you.

144
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:40,220
Thanks for agreeing to meet.

145
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:41,690
Now that your memory has returned,

146
00:08:42,560 --> 00:08:45,330
I felt we had to see each other
at least once.

147
00:08:45,760 --> 00:08:47,700
There's the matter
of Jin Ju's marriage...

148
00:08:47,770 --> 00:08:49,170
and the Temi Bio documentary.

149
00:08:49,270 --> 00:08:52,800
I know Jin Ju's marriage
was a means for revenge.

150
00:08:53,970 --> 00:08:57,280
Jin Ju told me not to do anything,
but I feel...

151
00:08:57,510 --> 00:08:58,780
I have to do something.

152
00:08:58,840 --> 00:09:00,650
Because you think
the marriage will end...

153
00:09:00,710 --> 00:09:02,010
once Jin Ju gets her revenge?

154
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:04,880
Is that why you got involved
with the Temi Bio documentary?

155
00:09:05,450 --> 00:09:08,550
I heard you even asked Producer Shin
to say that you commissioned it.

156
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:11,890
First of all, I have to protect
Jin Ju from my father.

157
00:09:13,260 --> 00:09:15,260
If there's anything
I can do to help,

158
00:09:15,260 --> 00:09:16,590
please let me know.

159
00:09:21,800 --> 00:09:22,800
Then,

160
00:09:23,430 --> 00:09:24,800
tell me about
President Kim Myung Hui.

161
00:09:25,500 --> 00:09:28,970
How did she live before joining
the Adele family 30 years ago?

162
00:09:29,570 --> 00:09:32,010
All I know is that
she grew up in an orphanage...

163
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:35,550
and worked as a nurse
before she met my father.

164
00:09:37,380 --> 00:09:40,250
But why are you asking
about my mother's past?

165
00:09:41,220 --> 00:09:42,350
Oh, that?

166
00:09:42,690 --> 00:09:46,220
She's now up against Jin Ju
over the Adele Group,

167
00:09:46,420 --> 00:09:48,560
so I'm curious
what kind of person she is.

168
00:09:49,230 --> 00:09:52,300
I'll look for the right moment
to persuade my mother.

169
00:09:59,400 --> 00:10:02,170
Jin Ju is looking for me.
I should get going.

170
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:03,440
Sure.

171
00:10:07,010 --> 00:10:08,010
Just a moment.

172
00:10:11,380 --> 00:10:12,450
What do you know...

173
00:10:13,020 --> 00:10:14,890
about Choi Yu Na?

174
00:10:15,450 --> 00:10:18,820
I have a feeling you know
how she's connected to the accident...

175
00:10:19,260 --> 00:10:20,490
from seven years ago.

176
00:10:26,430 --> 00:10:27,500
Choi Yu Na...

177
00:10:29,400 --> 00:10:32,400
lured Jin Ju into a trap
set by Chairman Park.

178
00:10:33,540 --> 00:10:36,240
When Jin Ju escaped the car
and begged for her life,

179
00:10:36,240 --> 00:10:37,610
she threw a rock at her...

180
00:10:39,540 --> 00:10:41,010
and even tried to kill her.

181
00:10:52,820 --> 00:10:54,130
Director Park Hyun Jun.

182
00:10:57,700 --> 00:10:58,700
What is this?

183
00:10:59,060 --> 00:11:01,030
Is it true that the wedding is off?

184
00:11:01,670 --> 00:11:03,900
Guests are saying
the bride ran away.

185
00:11:03,900 --> 00:11:04,900
What happened?

186
00:11:04,900 --> 00:11:06,400
Has the strategic marriage
between Adele Group...

187
00:11:06,470 --> 00:11:07,870
and JKL Partners been called off?

188
00:11:07,870 --> 00:11:10,010
- Please give us a comment.
- What are your future plans?

189
00:11:10,070 --> 00:11:12,180
Sir, could you please
answer our questions?

190
00:11:12,240 --> 00:11:13,380
Just one comment, please.

191
00:11:13,980 --> 00:11:16,580
What is all this nonsense?

192
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:19,650
My wedding went perfectly,

193
00:11:20,820 --> 00:11:22,890
and there is nothing wrong
with my marriage.

194
00:11:23,750 --> 00:11:26,120
Who on earth is spreading
such ridiculous rumors?

195
00:11:26,190 --> 00:11:29,030
They say it came from someone
inside Adele Group.

196
00:11:29,090 --> 00:11:31,560
- Someone inside the company?
- What are your plans going forward?

197
00:11:31,630 --> 00:11:33,530
Please answer our questions.

198
00:11:33,630 --> 00:11:35,100
Please tell us the truth.

199
00:11:35,700 --> 00:11:37,070
Just give us one comment.

200
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:39,000
Choi Yu Na!

201
00:11:48,480 --> 00:11:49,510
(Team Leader, Choi Yu Na)

202
00:11:52,550 --> 00:11:55,650
Choi Yu Na,
how could you do such a thing?

203
00:11:56,450 --> 00:11:58,920
After what you did to Jin Ju,
you still...

204
00:12:03,330 --> 00:12:06,630
Just you wait.
I'm going to make you pay...

205
00:12:07,830 --> 00:12:10,400
for what you did to Jin Ju.

206
00:12:13,070 --> 00:12:14,710
(Rumors of Adele Group
Marriage Annulment Spread)

207
00:12:14,770 --> 00:12:16,140
(Broken Engagement Shakes
the Business World)

208
00:12:20,140 --> 00:12:21,680
It was President Kim Myung Hui.

209
00:12:22,380 --> 00:12:26,220
Because we interfered with her appointment
as acting chairman,

210
00:12:26,220 --> 00:12:27,320
this is her way
of getting back at us.

211
00:12:29,250 --> 00:12:31,760
At this rate, the fight
for the successor position...

212
00:12:31,890 --> 00:12:34,430
between President Kim and us
will just drag on.

213
00:12:35,630 --> 00:12:38,560
If it does,
it'll be a burden in many ways.

214
00:12:38,630 --> 00:12:39,700
That's why...

215
00:12:39,700 --> 00:12:41,330
we have to look into her past,

216
00:12:41,600 --> 00:12:43,470
specifically who she was
as Kim Dan Hui.

217
00:12:43,930 --> 00:12:47,470
If we can find the right weakness,
we can win this.

218
00:12:47,710 --> 00:12:48,710
Kim Dan Hui?

219
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:52,110
I did some digging,
but I found nothing concrete.

220
00:12:52,180 --> 00:12:54,450
It'll be tough,
even for our intel team.

221
00:12:55,210 --> 00:12:57,410
It happened 30 years ago,
and there are no leads.

222
00:12:57,480 --> 00:12:59,120
Then we'll just have to find some.

223
00:12:59,850 --> 00:13:03,720
Why don't you start with the person
who called her "Kim Dan Hui?"

224
00:13:03,920 --> 00:13:04,920
Who?

225
00:13:06,890 --> 00:13:07,890
Secretary Jung?

226
00:13:08,190 --> 00:13:10,860
Yes. I'll meet with Oh Jung Ran...

227
00:13:10,930 --> 00:13:13,100
and ask about the situation
30 years ago.

228
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:20,940
You. Tell me about Myung Hui.

229
00:13:23,370 --> 00:13:26,080
Is her not feeling well
a cause for alarm?

230
00:13:26,340 --> 00:13:29,510
From what I can tell,
she's sick with rage.

231
00:13:30,680 --> 00:13:34,690
- Sick with rage?
- She fought to save you,

232
00:13:34,750 --> 00:13:37,250
only for you to suspect her because
of something Oh Jung Ran said.

233
00:13:37,250 --> 00:13:39,220
How unfair is that?

234
00:13:39,360 --> 00:13:41,090
Imagine saving someone,

235
00:13:41,230 --> 00:13:44,030
only to have them
accuse you afterward.

236
00:13:44,090 --> 00:13:46,060
Wouldn't that make your blood boil?

237
00:13:47,330 --> 00:13:52,100
She'll never feel
like saving them again.

238
00:13:53,840 --> 00:13:57,440
Wait, what?
The nerve of that little...

239
00:14:01,250 --> 00:14:02,250
She's furious?

240
00:14:02,610 --> 00:14:07,020
She'll never want to save me again?

241
00:14:12,790 --> 00:14:13,860
(Rumors of Adele Group
Marriage Annulment Spread)

242
00:14:13,920 --> 00:14:14,990
(Broken Engagement Shakes
the Business World)

243
00:14:15,130 --> 00:14:16,390
How are you feeling?

244
00:14:17,030 --> 00:14:20,100
- Are you okay?
- It was just a little bug.

245
00:14:20,300 --> 00:14:21,530
There's no need to worry.

246
00:14:22,500 --> 00:14:23,530
Anyway,

247
00:14:24,640 --> 00:14:25,970
how's Chairman Park?

248
00:14:26,900 --> 00:14:28,610
He's still thinking about you.

249
00:14:29,240 --> 00:14:31,410
Since you got angry,
which is so unlike you,

250
00:14:31,810 --> 00:14:33,840
he seemed a bit thrown off.

251
00:14:35,050 --> 00:14:36,410
At the end of the day,

252
00:14:37,510 --> 00:14:39,820
he has to trust me,
since I'm the one who saved him,

253
00:14:39,850 --> 00:14:42,820
not Oh Jung Ran,
who tried to kill him.

254
00:14:43,120 --> 00:14:45,860
I need to make him realize
that if I turn on him,

255
00:14:45,860 --> 00:14:47,220
he'll have no one else to trust.

256
00:14:47,560 --> 00:14:48,560
Exactly.

257
00:14:48,830 --> 00:14:50,760
It's about time
Chairman Park learned...

258
00:14:50,830 --> 00:14:52,460
to walk on eggshells around you.

259
00:15:00,170 --> 00:15:01,170
Sir.

260
00:15:01,940 --> 00:15:06,380
I heard you regained consciousness.
I'm glad to see you've recovered.

261
00:15:08,910 --> 00:15:10,050
You're glad?

262
00:15:11,550 --> 00:15:14,550
I'd have thought you were hoping
I wouldn't wake up.

263
00:15:15,090 --> 00:15:16,190
Oh, please.

264
00:15:16,990 --> 00:15:18,260
In fact,

265
00:15:18,720 --> 00:15:20,920
I really need you right now, sir.

266
00:15:23,860 --> 00:15:26,160
Ms. Choi, what brings you here?

267
00:15:27,100 --> 00:15:29,230
I came to congratulate him
on his recovery...

268
00:15:29,230 --> 00:15:31,100
and discuss something with him.

269
00:15:33,540 --> 00:15:34,540
Sir,

270
00:15:35,040 --> 00:15:39,110
Park Min Jun is still
investigating Temi Bio.

271
00:15:46,980 --> 00:15:48,220
What's with this reaction?

272
00:15:49,490 --> 00:15:51,690
I'm telling you,
Min Jun is investigating it.

273
00:15:54,530 --> 00:15:57,830
You claim to have feelings
for Director Park,

274
00:15:58,130 --> 00:16:00,200
yet you are trying to drive a wedge
between father and son.

275
00:16:01,070 --> 00:16:05,040
No, I'm just worried
about the both of you.

276
00:16:05,100 --> 00:16:07,170
We don't need your concern,
Ms. Choi.

277
00:16:08,610 --> 00:16:12,610
The chairman and I are already aware
of the situation and will handle it.

278
00:16:12,740 --> 00:16:15,550
What? You knew?

279
00:16:15,550 --> 00:16:17,310
Unbelievable.

280
00:16:18,680 --> 00:16:19,720
But...

281
00:16:20,820 --> 00:16:24,420
why do you keep meddling
in Temi Bio's affairs, Ms. Choi?

282
00:16:26,790 --> 00:16:29,160
- I was just...
- Quiet!

283
00:16:29,690 --> 00:16:32,730
If you mention Temi Bio
one more time,

284
00:16:33,200 --> 00:16:35,000
I'll rip your tongue out.

285
00:16:35,730 --> 00:16:37,870
Get out.
I can't stand the sight of you.

286
00:16:39,140 --> 00:16:41,110
- Sir?
- Leave.

287
00:16:53,820 --> 00:16:56,920
I'll handle the Temi Bio matter.

288
00:16:57,090 --> 00:16:59,490
Please stop tormenting Min Jun
with your suspicions.

289
00:17:01,060 --> 00:17:04,460
What do you mean I'm tormenting him?

290
00:17:04,760 --> 00:17:07,400
Why would I torment my own son?

291
00:17:09,230 --> 00:17:13,840
You go ahead and handle
the issue with Min Jun.

292
00:17:13,970 --> 00:17:14,970
Sure.

293
00:17:15,440 --> 00:17:18,680
I'm also handling
Hyun Jun and Chloe's marriage.

294
00:17:19,080 --> 00:17:23,010
Right. I already put you on that.

295
00:17:23,450 --> 00:17:26,450
Just handle it,
so it doesn't jeopardize...

296
00:17:27,720 --> 00:17:28,890
the exclusive development rights.

297
00:17:29,250 --> 00:17:30,250
Yes, sir.

298
00:17:44,230 --> 00:17:47,870
Chairman Park already knows,
so he'll stop it somehow.

299
00:17:49,710 --> 00:17:50,910
But what if...

300
00:17:51,240 --> 00:17:53,580
What if they find out
what I did too?

301
00:17:55,250 --> 00:17:56,680
Park Min Jun will never stop...

302
00:17:56,750 --> 00:17:58,720
even if it means
fighting the chairman.

303
00:18:00,020 --> 00:18:02,890
There must be a way to stop Min Jun.

304
00:18:03,490 --> 00:18:04,620
Someone...

305
00:18:08,360 --> 00:18:09,360
That's it.

306
00:18:10,390 --> 00:18:12,460
Even Park Min Jun...

307
00:18:13,260 --> 00:18:15,600
wouldn't risk hurting that person.

308
00:18:27,340 --> 00:18:29,880
Mom? Ms. Oh.

309
00:18:34,720 --> 00:18:36,420
You two again?

310
00:18:36,550 --> 00:18:37,720
Once again,

311
00:18:37,720 --> 00:18:40,860
I'm sure you don't have permission
from the chairman or Ms. Kim.

312
00:18:40,920 --> 00:18:43,930
Please leave
before I have to report you.

313
00:18:44,230 --> 00:18:45,230
Hey!

314
00:18:46,760 --> 00:18:48,370
Leave? As if.

315
00:18:48,900 --> 00:18:51,540
I have something important
to discuss with them.

316
00:18:51,540 --> 00:18:54,910
Unless you plan on saying this
to the chairman's face,

317
00:18:54,910 --> 00:18:56,040
let go of me.

318
00:18:56,110 --> 00:18:58,580
She's right, Jung Ran.
Don't fight it right now.

319
00:18:59,610 --> 00:19:03,110
If this gets any worse,
Hyun Jun will be in big trouble too.

320
00:19:03,210 --> 00:19:06,450
Mom, I mean Ms. Oh,
we'll head out for now.

321
00:19:06,550 --> 00:19:09,720
Don't worry about us. You take care.

322
00:19:14,420 --> 00:19:15,630
Let's go.

323
00:19:17,290 --> 00:19:18,860
Mrs. Ok.

324
00:19:18,860 --> 00:19:21,900
That's enough. Stop that.

325
00:19:26,170 --> 00:19:28,710
Mrs. Ok, how could you?

326
00:19:29,010 --> 00:19:30,610
After all the time
we've known each other,

327
00:19:30,670 --> 00:19:31,980
you've completely sided with them.

328
00:19:32,240 --> 00:19:35,110
Drugging her with sleeping pills
and now watching her every move?

329
00:19:36,680 --> 00:19:38,680
I had no idea you were like this.

330
00:19:39,480 --> 00:19:41,220
How could you not know?

331
00:19:41,490 --> 00:19:44,090
Because you were so clueless,
I'm stuck in this mess too.

332
00:19:45,060 --> 00:19:46,260
I knew what she was like...

333
00:19:46,260 --> 00:19:49,760
the moment she started smirking
and getting on my nerves.

334
00:19:49,930 --> 00:19:53,660
Just wait until I get out of here.
I'll make you pay.

335
00:19:56,400 --> 00:19:57,800
Doesn't your conscience bother you?

336
00:19:58,240 --> 00:19:59,640
What?

337
00:20:01,410 --> 00:20:06,080
I was just saying how great
these new knitting needles are.

338
00:20:06,210 --> 00:20:08,050
They're so smooth...

339
00:20:08,850 --> 00:20:10,510
they don't even poke your skin.

340
00:20:10,510 --> 00:20:11,950
Who do you think
you're messing with?

341
00:20:12,450 --> 00:20:15,190
You should be careful.
Since they're new...

342
00:20:15,190 --> 00:20:17,120
I'm not used to them yet.

343
00:20:17,120 --> 00:20:19,860
It'd be terrible if I accidentally
poked something I shouldn't.

344
00:20:32,800 --> 00:20:35,240
How much longer do I have
to stay here like this?

345
00:20:35,940 --> 00:20:38,440
What's going on outside?

346
00:20:39,040 --> 00:20:41,450
What about Temi Bio and Kim Dan Hui?

347
00:20:43,050 --> 00:20:44,680
This is so frustrating.

348
00:20:47,480 --> 00:20:49,520
If we want to look into
the Kim Dan Hui situation,

349
00:20:50,190 --> 00:20:53,390
there's a lot we need to confirm
with your mother.

350
00:20:55,130 --> 00:20:57,890
Our marriage,
and President Kim's weakness.

351
00:20:58,300 --> 00:21:01,370
- None of this is easy.
- To secure our marriage...

352
00:21:02,000 --> 00:21:06,000
and find out what happened
30 years ago from your mother,

353
00:21:08,440 --> 00:21:11,880
I think we'll have
to go down that road.

354
00:21:12,780 --> 00:21:14,540
What road?

355
00:21:15,380 --> 00:21:16,780
Whatever it is, just tell me.

356
00:21:23,490 --> 00:21:24,490
- Have a good one.
- Thank you.

357
00:21:24,550 --> 00:21:25,560
Take care.

358
00:21:25,620 --> 00:21:27,360
(Bongmyeong Neighborhood Coffee)

359
00:21:27,690 --> 00:21:29,930
(All-in-one Cafe)

360
00:21:30,460 --> 00:21:32,860
- Welcome...
- Welcome.

361
00:21:35,670 --> 00:21:36,900
What do you want?

362
00:21:38,740 --> 00:21:40,900
It's been a while,
and that's quite...

363
00:21:41,440 --> 00:21:42,910
the welcome.

364
00:21:42,970 --> 00:21:45,810
Right. It's been a while.
So what do you want?

365
00:21:45,880 --> 00:21:49,380
What else would I be here for?
I came for coffee.

366
00:21:50,880 --> 00:21:54,580
By the way, I don't see your sister.

367
00:21:56,690 --> 00:21:58,160
Doesn't she usually stop by
around this time?

368
00:21:58,360 --> 00:22:01,060
If you came here for coffee,
why are you asking...

369
00:22:01,220 --> 00:22:03,830
about my sister
before you even look at the menu?

370
00:22:03,890 --> 00:22:06,630
Nice one, boss. That was sharp.

371
00:22:11,170 --> 00:22:13,470
- Hey, James.
- Hey.

372
00:22:14,340 --> 00:22:15,610
Secretary Jung.

373
00:22:16,740 --> 00:22:18,140
Yoon Jung,
place your order and leave.

374
00:22:18,640 --> 00:22:21,480
I'll deliver it to you.
Just go already.

375
00:22:21,780 --> 00:22:23,050
Why should I...

376
00:22:23,810 --> 00:22:25,280
when James is here?

377
00:22:27,920 --> 00:22:28,920
What?

378
00:22:29,650 --> 00:22:32,390
Perfect timing.
I was hoping to see you.

379
00:22:32,920 --> 00:22:34,660
You wanted to see me?

380
00:22:37,690 --> 00:22:40,460
Yes. Are you free today?

381
00:22:40,760 --> 00:22:44,270
Even if you're busy, make some time.
Let's grab a drink.

382
00:22:44,840 --> 00:22:48,640
Wait a minute.
What do you think you're doing?

383
00:22:48,640 --> 00:22:50,270
Sounds like
she's asking him on a date.

384
00:22:50,670 --> 00:22:52,410
A date? No way.

385
00:22:53,910 --> 00:22:56,180
Are you in or out?

386
00:22:57,850 --> 00:23:01,520
Sure, let's go. Shall we?

387
00:23:03,920 --> 00:23:06,620
- Wait. Where are you going?
- Move.

388
00:23:06,760 --> 00:23:09,860
Hey, wait. Seriously?

389
00:23:10,560 --> 00:23:12,000
I'm sorry to ask,

390
00:23:12,500 --> 00:23:14,030
but can you close up the shop today?

391
00:23:14,030 --> 00:23:16,370
- What?
- Hold on. Wait for me!

392
00:23:26,780 --> 00:23:30,910
I have to find out everything I can
about Kim Myung Hui and Kim Dan Hui.

393
00:23:35,320 --> 00:23:37,820
Tailing them didn't get me much.

394
00:23:38,190 --> 00:23:40,390
I'll get him drunk
and loosen his tongue.

395
00:23:40,720 --> 00:23:43,930
I need to find out
if Chloe really lost her memory.

396
00:23:45,030 --> 00:23:46,400
There's only one rule.

397
00:23:46,400 --> 00:23:48,370
If you can't answer, you drink?

398
00:23:48,430 --> 00:23:49,730
Then I'll go first.

399
00:23:50,670 --> 00:23:55,470
I heard you're a corporate raider.
Is that true?

400
00:23:56,970 --> 00:23:58,580
A raider?

401
00:23:58,580 --> 00:24:01,140
It's a perfectly
legitimate business.

402
00:24:02,280 --> 00:24:05,480
- You're quite the smooth talker.
- Now it's my turn.

403
00:24:05,820 --> 00:24:06,820
Secretary Jung,

404
00:24:06,850 --> 00:24:09,390
how long have you worked
with President Kim Myung Hui?

405
00:24:10,120 --> 00:24:14,020
Since she first came to Adele.
So about 20 years.

406
00:24:14,190 --> 00:24:17,190
After that long,
aren't you two basically friends?

407
00:24:18,230 --> 00:24:20,930
Friends? Don't be ridiculous.

408
00:24:21,330 --> 00:24:25,340
We have a professional relationship.
Boss and secretary. That's it.

409
00:24:26,540 --> 00:24:27,840
All right, next question.

410
00:24:29,540 --> 00:24:32,810
Did Chloe really lose her memory?

411
00:24:33,040 --> 00:24:35,310
She married a man
she doesn't even remember.

412
00:24:35,380 --> 00:24:37,610
One question at a time, please.

413
00:24:37,610 --> 00:24:39,450
That's not an answer.

414
00:24:39,950 --> 00:24:41,890
- Drink up.
- No, I was just...

415
00:24:44,490 --> 00:24:45,490
The question...

416
00:24:54,330 --> 00:24:59,470
Anyway, how did President Kim
meet Chairman Park?

417
00:25:01,340 --> 00:25:02,840
How would I know that?

418
00:25:04,840 --> 00:25:07,310
If you can't answer, then drink up.

419
00:25:10,310 --> 00:25:11,310
What is he up to?

420
00:25:12,350 --> 00:25:15,720
Is he trying to dig into
Dan Hui's past?

421
00:25:19,190 --> 00:25:20,520
Okay, next question.

422
00:25:20,920 --> 00:25:24,760
Chloe is married now,
so what's her next move?

423
00:25:31,800 --> 00:25:33,400
I get it now.

424
00:25:33,670 --> 00:25:36,510
You're trying to get the lowdown
on Chloe.

425
00:25:51,390 --> 00:25:54,860
Hey, pull it together, will you?

426
00:25:55,630 --> 00:25:57,060
Trying to pump me for information...

427
00:25:57,690 --> 00:25:59,600
when you can't
even hold your liquor?

428
00:26:01,460 --> 00:26:04,770
Tell me about it.
He picked the wrong opponent.

429
00:26:09,770 --> 00:26:13,640
When did President Kim Myung Hui
become Kim Myung Hui?

430
00:26:15,150 --> 00:26:16,180
Drink.

431
00:26:16,710 --> 00:26:19,950
Hey, mister. Drink up.

432
00:26:30,390 --> 00:26:33,230
She seems absolutely furious.

433
00:26:33,660 --> 00:26:37,170
With things this uncertain,

434
00:26:37,730 --> 00:26:40,440
if Myung Hui abandons me too,

435
00:26:41,170 --> 00:26:43,010
I'll have no one left to trust.

436
00:26:48,680 --> 00:26:52,020
Come on, please don't be angry.

437
00:26:57,020 --> 00:26:59,920
I've been thinking about it,

438
00:27:00,260 --> 00:27:03,290
and the only person I can trust
is you, Myung Hui.

439
00:27:03,530 --> 00:27:07,030
I was just briefly swayed
by Oh Jung Ran's manipulation.

440
00:27:07,460 --> 00:27:09,900
I wasn't really doubting you.

441
00:27:10,130 --> 00:27:12,500
Once Min Jun handles
the documentary issue,

442
00:27:12,570 --> 00:27:15,040
I'll announce him
as my successor right away.

443
00:27:15,110 --> 00:27:18,410
And at the next board meeting,

444
00:27:20,140 --> 00:27:23,650
you'll be appointed
the acting chairman. Okay?

445
00:27:24,350 --> 00:27:25,820
Once my divorce is finalized,

446
00:27:25,920 --> 00:27:27,680
we'll register our marriage
immediately.

447
00:27:28,550 --> 00:27:29,890
Register our marriage?

448
00:27:30,820 --> 00:27:34,490
You asked me to divorce her
and marry you.

449
00:27:36,090 --> 00:27:37,760
We'll officially
register our marriage,

450
00:27:38,530 --> 00:27:41,500
and you'll become the lady
of the Adele family.

451
00:27:45,270 --> 00:27:46,800
Sorry to interrupt your meal,

452
00:27:47,570 --> 00:27:49,740
but I think
you should come see this.

453
00:27:56,950 --> 00:27:57,950
Wait.

454
00:28:00,620 --> 00:28:03,220
What's all this?

455
00:28:04,790 --> 00:28:05,790
What?

456
00:28:11,360 --> 00:28:14,200
What do you two think you're doing?

457
00:28:14,630 --> 00:28:16,530
Since we were living separately
even though we were married,

458
00:28:16,970 --> 00:28:18,570
it seems to have caused
some misunderstandings.

459
00:28:19,470 --> 00:28:21,400
I'm tired of
all these bizarre articles.

460
00:28:22,040 --> 00:28:23,770
They're really getting on my nerves.

461
00:28:28,480 --> 00:28:31,510
I'm going to show everyone
how solid our marriage is.

462
00:28:32,280 --> 00:28:34,780
We'll begin our married life
in Hyun Jun's room.

463
00:28:37,050 --> 00:28:38,120
Says who?

464
00:28:38,920 --> 00:28:40,290
Get out right now!

465
00:28:41,420 --> 00:28:44,730
Don't upset the chairman,
and leave this instant.

466
00:28:46,660 --> 00:28:48,300
If you kick me out like this,

467
00:28:49,030 --> 00:28:50,130
you're going to regret it.

468
00:28:52,000 --> 00:28:53,000
Regret it?

469
00:28:55,670 --> 00:28:57,940
What are you scheming this time?

470
00:29:13,760 --> 00:29:15,760
(BIT Life, President Kim Myung Hui)

471
00:29:24,370 --> 00:29:26,400
(Bit Life President, Kim Myung Hui)

472
00:29:31,510 --> 00:29:32,680
(What Led to the Car Explosion?)

473
00:29:32,740 --> 00:29:34,640
(Suspicions Grow Over
CEO Baek Jun Gi's Death)

474
00:29:35,850 --> 00:29:36,950
I'll tell Chairman Park...

475
00:29:37,610 --> 00:29:40,380
that President Kim
has suspicious documents...

476
00:29:41,420 --> 00:29:43,690
and make sure files on the car crash
from seven years ago...

477
00:29:44,250 --> 00:29:46,920
and CEO Baek Jun Gi are found.

478
00:29:48,090 --> 00:29:50,460
Then Chairman Park
will completely freak out.

479
00:29:52,330 --> 00:29:53,330
And Park Min Jun...

480
00:29:54,100 --> 00:29:56,430
will be too concerned
about his mother getting hurt...

481
00:29:57,700 --> 00:30:01,040
to dig into the incident
from seven years ago.

482
00:30:01,670 --> 00:30:03,610
(Bit Life President, Kim Myung Hui)

483
00:30:07,610 --> 00:30:11,150
I'll have to hide this somewhere
so Ms. Kim doesn't notice.

484
00:30:11,980 --> 00:30:13,180
(Humangen Diagnostic Center)

485
00:30:13,220 --> 00:30:14,250
Humangen?

486
00:30:15,290 --> 00:30:16,320
A DNA test?

487
00:30:17,290 --> 00:30:19,360
(Humangen Diagnostic Center)

488
00:30:24,190 --> 00:30:25,700
(Humangen Diagnostic Center)

489
00:30:29,330 --> 00:30:32,340
Scheming? That's a little harsh.

490
00:30:33,270 --> 00:30:34,570
I'm just saying
that if you kick us out,

491
00:30:34,840 --> 00:30:37,470
there could be problems.

492
00:30:38,340 --> 00:30:40,210
What problems?

493
00:30:50,990 --> 00:30:52,190
(Joint
Mineral Development Agreement)

494
00:30:53,420 --> 00:30:56,460
This is a contract
between the Adele Group and JKL Partners.

495
00:30:56,660 --> 00:30:58,290
If the joint development project
is canceled,

496
00:30:59,100 --> 00:31:01,930
the party at fault
has to pay a penalty.

497
00:31:03,730 --> 00:31:06,300
Your mother, Oh Jung Ran,

498
00:31:06,300 --> 00:31:08,710
used a forged power of attorney
to sign that contract.

499
00:31:08,710 --> 00:31:10,410
The contract itself is void.

500
00:31:11,940 --> 00:31:13,380
Well, about that...

501
00:31:14,410 --> 00:31:15,880
They say that's a matter
for the courts to decide.

502
00:31:17,410 --> 00:31:18,720
That's enough, Hyun Jun.

503
00:31:19,880 --> 00:31:21,650
They're going to get the wrong idea.

504
00:31:23,420 --> 00:31:27,360
We're not here to fight.
We're just asking you to accept us.

505
00:31:27,990 --> 00:31:30,760
Please accept me
as the Adele family's daughter-in-law.

506
00:31:31,860 --> 00:31:34,730
Let's be a family
and try to get along.

507
00:31:35,630 --> 00:31:36,630
Father.

508
00:31:39,370 --> 00:31:40,640
And...

509
00:31:40,770 --> 00:31:42,210
Lady Kim.

510
00:31:45,480 --> 00:31:47,280
(Humangen Diagnostic Center)

511
00:31:53,750 --> 00:31:54,920
(DNA Parentage Test Report)

512
00:31:55,050 --> 00:31:56,790
(Subject 1: Park Hyun Jun,
Subject 2: Song Geun Tae)

513
00:31:59,860 --> 00:32:01,320
(The results are indicative
of a paternal relationship.)

514
00:32:04,860 --> 00:32:05,860
What the...

515
00:32:06,860 --> 00:32:08,600
Park Hyun Jun is Song Geun Tae's...

516
00:32:11,030 --> 00:32:12,470
He's Driver Song's son?

517
00:32:38,800 --> 00:32:41,800
(Pearl in Red)

518
00:32:42,030 --> 00:32:45,270
You stole Jin Ju's life.
Don't you feel any shame or guilt?

519
00:32:45,800 --> 00:32:48,940
I'm going to expose
every single evil thing you've done...

520
00:32:49,670 --> 00:32:52,240
and make sure you suffer for it.

521
00:32:52,640 --> 00:32:53,640
The rock.

522
00:32:53,710 --> 00:32:55,780
Only Baek Jin Ju and I
knew about that.

523
00:32:56,510 --> 00:32:57,850
I have to stop Park Min Jun.

524
00:32:58,380 --> 00:32:59,850
Maybe I can use this.

525
00:32:59,950 --> 00:33:01,150
What does it say?

526
00:33:01,150 --> 00:33:03,420
Apparently, Chloe's testing me.

527
00:33:03,720 --> 00:33:05,660
She's practically challenging me
to escape.

528
00:33:05,920 --> 00:33:07,790
What? I know you're clever,

529
00:33:07,790 --> 00:33:09,530
but how are you going
to get out of here?

530
00:33:10,060 --> 00:33:12,060
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
